Walk-in-interview for JRF/SRF Project Positions: 3rd August, 2016 at 9-00 AM in the School of Information Technology, 2nd Floor, Takshashila Building, IIT Kharagpur

3 JRF/SRF positions open in the SWAN Group ( http://www.sit.iitkgp.ernet.in/~smisra/swan/index.html ) for immediate recruitment. Candidates should have M.Tech or equivalent degree in CSE/IT/ECE/EE/Instrumentation/Mechatronics with preferably two years of research experience and high percentage of marks throughout the career starting from Class X. Candidates with BTech degree but with excellent percentage of marks throughout and GATE score may also be considered. E-mail smisra.editor@gmail.com if you feel you qualify and have interest to work in the broad domain of Internet of Things (IoT).
See the following advertisement links and apply:
http://www.iitkgp.ac.in/topfiles/sric_job_details.php?serial=3279
http://www.iitkgp.ac.in/topfiles/sric_job_details.php?serial=3280

These positions are PhD linked. So, the accepted candidates would have to qualify a separate Institute-level admission test for PhD.

